Sepertinya rekan-rekan yang lain
tidak akan mengalami kesulitan.

41
00:04:06,140 --> 00:04:07,730
Para prajurit Dragonewt!

42
00:04:07,730 --> 00:04:09,480
Ikuti aku!

43
00:04:10,130 --> 00:04:10,850
Serangan musuh!

44
00:04:11,700 --> 00:04:13,190
Ber-Bersiaplah!

45
00:04:13,190 --> 00:04:15,070
Formasi pertahanan serangan udara!

46
00:04:15,070 --> 00:04:17,000
Me-Mereka Dragonewt?

