102
00:08:42,420 --> 00:08:45,330
Semua masalah bisa diatasi
kalau penyebabnya diketahui.

103
00:08:45,330 --> 00:08:46,670
Menarik.

104
00:08:46,670 --> 00:08:50,430
Bagaimana kalau kita saling mengadu
kemampuan berpedang saja?

105
00:08:51,380 --> 00:08:52,510
